# Google Apps Script Web App URL
# 1. Open https://script.google.com and create a new project
# 2. Paste the script from docs/superpowers/plans/2026-06-15-security-seo-cookies.md (Task 7)
# 3. Change the recipient email inside the script to the real Frasco inbox
# 4. Click Deploy > New Deployment > Web App
#    - Execute as: Me
#    - Who has access: Anyone
# 5. Copy the Web App URL and paste it below
GOOGLE_SCRIPT_URL=https://script.google.com/macros/s/REPLACE_WITH_YOUR_DEPLOYMENT_ID/exec
